  <section>
    <h2>What's in it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Salary-transfer log.</strong> Every UAE bank that changed an offer this week — new tier, raised threshold, expired bonus, voucher swap.</li>
      <li><strong>Cards in motion.</strong> Annual fee, FX fee, welcome bonus or eligibility changes that landed this week, plus a one-line take.</li>
      <li><strong>Miles redemption of the week.</strong> One sweet spot we found that's actually bookable, not theoretical.</li>
      <li><strong>One deal worth your time.</strong> Lifestyle-culture editor's pick — only the ones we'd take ourselves.</li>
      <li><strong>One number.</strong> A figure from the UAE banking / loyalty world worth thinking about, briefly.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What's not in it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Affiliate links disguised as picks. The asterisk system is the firewall — it'll be in the brief unchanged.</li>
      <li>Sponsored slots. The brief is unfunded.</li>
      <li>Inbox filler. If a Friday has nothing material, it's a short email — not a long one with padding.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

